<wfdescription>&lt;p&gt;In this single-class activity, students apply the principal of superposition to two new contexts. While hearing a sinusoidal signal feeding 2 speakers, students walk around the room to experience constructive Interference and destructive Interference and gain a better understanding of these concepts. See a full description &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.saltise.ca/activity/live-demonstrations-of-beats-and-interference-of-sound/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</wfdescription>
