<id>7</id>
<lefticon>undefined</lefticon>
<righticon>curation</righticon>
<column>OOCI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;p&gt;Prepare to bring the following equipment:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;two signal generators,&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;two speakers,&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;one oscilloscope with a microphone connected to it,&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;a computer with a graphical display of volume as a function of frequency (eg. a pasco sound sensor used with a fft plot)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;tuning forks&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;plastic pipes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;instruments (optional)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Note: Optionally, invite students to bring their instruments to class that day.&lt;/p&gt;</textHTML>
